Watch out for enemies: the beach ball brothers, the frog, the flea, and the evil Dr. Flatten are all after you. Keep an eye out for the friendly Tick-Tock clock - if you land on the same block as him, he'll make sure no enemies appear for a while! If you get into trouble on the edges of the pyramid, you can use the buckets as a quick escape route.<br><br>
<font class=b>Tips:</font><br>
- Use the buckets to escape to the top of the castle.<br>
- Try to get an enemy to jump off the castle by heading towards the edge.<br>
- Press S to turn the sound effects on and off and M to turn the music on and off.<br>
- Press P to toggle the game pause.<br><br>































































